'''Ahidrujin''' ( s [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tinglizt]] : Hydrogen , s [[Tutlayt Tafransist|tfranṣiṣt]] : Hydrogène) iga t [[Afrḍis akimyan|ufrḍis]] akimi lli mu gan tasdugmt n H d uṭṭun afrḍas 1.  Netta ad kullu ifssusen ɣ umaḍal. Ɣ ''standard conditions'' hidrojin ar ittgga gaz n snat ''molecules'' d ar ttggan '''H2'''. Iga war-ikʷlan d war-aḍu, ur igi ''toxic'', d ar ijdder s zzerb.

'''Ahidrujin''' ad igguten ɣ umaḍal, slahwant akkʷ lliɣ iɣʷi 75% n tfekka ''(matter)''. Itran zun d tafukt nneɣ ur gan-t amer '''Ahidrojin''' ɣ ''the plasma state''. Agudi n hidrojin ɣ wakal ar ittmun d ifrḍisen yaḍni ar skarn ''molecules'' zun d  aman neɣ-dd ''organic compounds''.<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hydrogen</ref>
